<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٧٩١ - د ش د ش]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>دشدشَ يُدشدش، دشدشةً، فهو مُدشدِش، والمفعول مُدشدَش<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• دشدش الزُّجاجَ ونحوَه:</span> كسَّره <span class="c1">"دشدش الكأسَ"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>